Q23. Write AJAX program to read contact.dat file and print the contents of the
file in a tabular format when the user clicks on print button. Contact.dat file
should contain srno, name, residence number, mobile number, Address.
[Enter at least 3 record in contact.dat file]
  
Answer:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

1st Page.php
// Create contact.dat file from terminal
<?php
$f=fopen("contact.dat","r");
echo"<table border=1>";
echo"<tr><th>Srno</th> <th>Name</th> <th>Residence no</th> <th>Mno</th>
<th>Address</th></tr>";
while($row=fscanf($f,"%s %s %s %s %s"))
{
echo"<tr>";
foreach($row as $r)
{
echo"<td>$r</td>";
}
echo"</tr>";
}
echo"</table>";
fclose($f);
?>

2nd Page.php

<html>
<head>
<script>
function load()
{
var x=new XMLHttpRequest();
x.open("GET","Q23.php",true);
x.send();
x.onreadystatechange=function()
{
if(x.readyState==4 && x.status==200)
{
document.getElementById("res").innerHTML=x.responseText;
}
}
}
</script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="res"></div>
<button onclick="load()">print</button>
</body>
</html>
